===[[Season 2]]===
[[Jaqen H'ghar]], one of [[Yoren]]'s new recruits for the [[Night's Watch]], claims to be from Lorath.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Night Lands]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

When [[Cersei Lannister]] meets [[Shae]] for the first time, she recognizes from her accent that she is a Lorathi. Cersei states that she is familiar with the accent because she once had a handmaiden who was from Lorath.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Blackwater]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
